  = must: keep ignored runtime surfaces out of any candidate commit
  = must: keep broad .sop dirty state out of the RH first-bookend commit unless explicitly selected
  = must: recommend a scope but not stage or commit without explicit direction
  = must: preserve no-commit status clearly
